content.rendered:
Directed by Girish A.D.

Written by Dinoy Poulose

Cast Vineeth Sreenivasan (Ravi Padmanabhan). Mathew Thomas (Jaison). Anaswara Rajan (Keerthy). Naslen (Melvin (as Nalsen K. Gafoor)). Vaisakh Vijayan (Dennis). Franco Francis (Linto). Irshad (School Principal). Dinoy Poulose (Joyson). Nisha Sarangh (Keerthy’s Mother). Sajin Cherukayil (Satheesh). Shabareesh Varma (Siju). Sree Renjini (Aswathy). Binny Rinky Benjamin (Bindhu) . Girish A.D.(Bike Rider (Cameo)). Anagha Ajith (Maneesha). Arshad Ali (Vijil). Suhail M. Ali (Suhail). Aiswarya Anilkumar (Keerthy’s Sister). Arun Antony (Vinu). Akshay Ashokan (Humanities Class Boy 2). Baby (Lilly). Anagha Biju (Rekha). Sandeep Chandran (Jaison’s Local Friend 2 (Conductor)). Rama Devi (Jaison’s Mother). Dhanya (PT Teacher). Varun Dhara (Jaison’s Local Friend 1). Sreelakshmi G.(Tessy). James George (Humanities Class Boy 1). Jilna George (Jilna). Midhun Gopinadh (Basil). Vazhoor Jose (Cricket Commentator). Vigil Jose (Vigilance Team). Arjun K.(Bibin). Reneesh K.R.(Sandeep). Vishnu Raj K.R.(Rahul). Nandakumar Koratty (Jaison’s Father). Aravind Vinod Kumar (Priest). Aiswarya Laiby (Aiswarya). Tessy Jolly M.(Dennis’ Mother). Vishnu Mukundan (George). Clinton Perera (Kappiar). Gopika Ramesh (Stephy).Remadevi. M.K. Roy (Keerthy’s Father). Dileep Sasidharan (Bike Rider). Kichu Tellus (Antony). Akash Unnikrishnan (Sarath). Vineeth Vasudevan (Tour Guide). Vineeth Vishwam (Anto). George Wincent (Justin)

Languages Malayalam

Producers Shebin Backer. Jomon T. John. Shameer Muhammed

Production Plan J Studio. Shebin Backer Production
